        <num>13-4-41</num>
        <content>
          <p>Payment by mail shall be made at the risk of the debtor unless done by direction, either express or implied, of the creditor or his agent.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2807; Code 1868, § 2815; Code 1873, § 2866; Code 1882, § 2866; Civil Code 1895, § 3719; Civil Code 1910, § 4313; Code 1933, § 20-1003.)</p>
